Introduction

Jeon Wonwoo is the lead rapper and sub-vocalist of the boy group SEVENTEEN under Pledis Entertainment. He is also a member of the group's rap unit.

Wonwoo debuted as a member of SEVENTEEN on May 26, 2015, with the mini-album 17 Carat. He also made his debut in the sub-unit JEONGHAN X WONWOO on June 17th, 2024 with their single "This Man"
